MagicNoNumberedHeadings extension was created so as to resolve
http://bugzilla.wikimedia.org/7832

What does this extension do?

  This extension adds a Magic Word __NONUMBEREDHEADINGS__ to the parser.
  If an article contains this MagicWord, automatic numbering of the
  headings in this page is disabled, regardless of the user preference
  setting.

Usage

  Add "__NONUMBEREDHEADINGS__" to any article.

Installation

  Add this line towards the end of your $IP/LocalSettings.php

  require_once($IP.'/extensions/MagicNoNumberedHeadings/MagicNoNumberedHeadings.php');

  Note, $IP is the MediaWiki installation directory.

